View Menu: Displays the menu items and prices.
Add to Cart: Prompts the user to choose an item and quantity. Updates the cart accordingly.
Remove from Cart: Allows the user to remove a specific quantity or the entire item from the cart.
View Cart: Displays all items in the cart, their quantities, individual prices, and the total price.
Place Order: Confirms the order and clears the cart.
Exit: Ends the program.
